<Base title="Privacy Policy - waglesworld" description="How waglesworld.com handles your data.">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: February 2026</p>

  <p>This site is a personal blog run by Mihir Wagle. I respect your privacy and collect as little data as possible. Here's what you should know.</p>

  <h2>What I collect</h2>

  <h3>Newsletter</h3>
  <p>If you subscribe to the newsletter, your email address is collected and stored by <a href="https://kit.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kit.com</a> (formerly ConvertKit). I use it only to send you new posts. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in every email.</p>

  <h3>Comments</h3>
  <p>Comments are powered by <a href="https://github.com/giscus/giscus" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Giscus</a>, which uses GitHub Discussions. To leave a comment, you sign in with your GitHub account. Your comment data is stored by GitHub under their <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a>.</p>

  <h2>What I don't collect</h2>
  <p>This site does not use analytics, advertising, tracking pixels, or fingerprinting. There is no server-side data collection beyond what the hosting provider (Vercel) logs for standard web serving.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>This site does not set first-party cookies. Third-party services (Giscus, Kit.com) may set their own cookies when you interact with comments or the newsletter form. The KaTeX CSS is loaded from jsdelivr CDN, which does not set cookies.</p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Kit.com</strong> — newsletter email collection and delivery</li>
    <li><strong>GitHub / Giscus</strong> — comments system</li>
    <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — site hosting</li>
    <li><strong>Sanity</strong> — content management (no user-facing data collection)</li>
    <li><strong>jsdelivr</strong> — CDN for math rendering CSS</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>You can request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal data I hold. To make a request or ask questions, email me at <strong>mihir@waglesworld.com</strong>.</p>

